1704760992.text: "The Bcl-2 family consists of both cell death promoters and preventers, including the anti-apoptotic proteins Bcl-2, Bcl- xL, Mcl-1, A1/Bfl -1 and Bcl-W, and the pro apoptotic members Bax, Bak, Bad, Bik, Bid, Hrk and Bok [XREF_BIBR]."
